description:
Debian 12.8 is now available for download with 68 bug fixes and 50 security updates for the Debian GNU/Linux 12 “Bookworm” operating system series.

The post Debian 12.8 “Bookworm” Released with 68 Bug Fixes and 50 Security Updates appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Debian 12.8 “Bookworm” Released with 68 Bug Fixes and 50 Security Updates
